, "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Resource finding function, also available in templates.\n\nTries to find a resource, will force SSL depending on\n`BOOTSTRAP_CDN_FORCE_SSL` settings.\n\n```\nparam filename\n\nFile to find a URL for.\n\nparam cdn\n\nName of the CDN to use.\n\nparam use_minified'\n\nIf set to True/False, use/don't use\nminified. If None, honors\nBOOTSTRAP_USE_MINIFIED.\n\nparam local\n\nIf True, uses the local-CDN when\nBOOTSTRAP_SERVE_LOCAL is enabled. If False, uses\nthe static-CDN instead.\n\nreturn\n\nA URL.\n```\n"]}], "variables": [{"name": "flask_bootstrap.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_bootstrap.BOOTSTRAP_VERSION", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_bootstrap.JQUERY_VERSION", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_bootstrap.HTML5SHIV_VERSION", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_bootstrap.RESPONDJS_VERSION", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "flask_bootstrap.CDN", "bases": ["object"], "methods": [{"name": "flask_bootstrap.CDN.get_resource_url", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "filename", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Return resource url for filename."]}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Base class for CDN objects."]}, {"name": "flask_bootstrap.StaticCDN", "bases": ["object"], "methods": [{"name": "flask_bootstrap.StaticCDN.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "static_endpoint", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "rev", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_bootstrap.StaticCDN.get_resource_url", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "filename", "type": null, "default": null}]